{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-8","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-cafe-menu","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 8","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U prethodnom koraku, koristili ste <dfn>selektor tipa</dfn> da biste kreirali stil za element <code>h1</code>. Postavite sadržaj elemenata <code>h2</code> i <code>p</code> u sredinu dodajući novi selektor tipa za svaki od njih na postojeći element <code>style</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"5f3477ae9675db8bb7655b30","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-cafe-menu/step-8"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n  <head>\n    <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n    <title>Cafe Menu</title>\n    <style>\n      h1 {\n        text-align: center;\n      }\n      \n    </style>\n  </head>\n  <body>\n    <main>\n      <h1>CAMPER CAFE</h1>\n      <p>Est. 2020</p>\n      <section>\n        <h2>Coffee</h2>\n      </section>\n    </main>\n  </body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[9,11],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Ne smijete mijenjati postojeći selektor za <code>h1</code>.</p>","testString":"const hasH1 = new __helpers.CSSHelp(document).getStyle('h1');\nassert.exists(hasH1);"},{"text":"<p>Ne smete dodati novu oznaku za <code>style</code>. Dodajte nove pravila za CSS na postojeću oznaku <code>style</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.isAtMost(document.querySelectorAll('style').length, 2);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da dodate novi selektor za <code>h2</code>.</p>","t